        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Oh let the sun beat down upon my face </l>
          <l>Stars to fill my dream </l>
          <l>I am a traveler of both time and space </l>
          <l>To be where I have been </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>As the dust that floats high in June </l>
          <l>When movin' through Kashmir. </l>
          <l>With no provision but an open face </l>
          <l>Along the straits of fear </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>I been flying </l>
          <l>There ain't no denyin' </l>
          <l>Flying, flying </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>All I see turns to brown </l>
          <l>All I see turns to brown </l>
          <l>As the sun burns the ground </l>
          <l>Burns, burns </l>
          <l>And my eyes fill with sand </l>
          <l>My eyes fill with sand </l>
          <l>As I scan this wasted land </l>
          <l>This wasted land </l>
        </lg>
